<br>
Basically, the very fact that the rampage list is not really actually tied to the main hate list is why we're the best rampage tanks. (Well, rogues could do it too, I suppose, as could rangers on something where jolt/cinder jolt lands all the time) Also, the fact that we can stonestance frequently and can feign if we get low HP until a heal lands, with a good chance of getting right back onto the rampage list when we stand. Note: I HAVE seen many cases where feigning causes rampage aggro to move to the next person on the rampage list and stay there. So, it can bounce around some.<br>
<br>
 <p>-Arlos the Disciple <BR>
Legacy of Steel <BR>
